title: Kayray's Storytime
creator: Various
description: LibriVox recording of Kayray's Storytime, by Various. Read by Kara Shallenberg. A collection of my favorite short children's stories and rhymes. Each book can be found online at http://gutenberg.org if you wish to look at the wonderful pictures while you listen! (Summary by Kara) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (74MB)
